title: Windows Vista Ultimate 64-bit Danish incl. ServicePack 1 and Act
description:
Windows Vista Ultimate 64-bit Danish - With Service Pack 1

1. Burn ISO into a DVD disc (fx with PowerISO, Alcohol 120, Nero or whatever!)
2. Install OS from the bootable DVD. (DON&#039;T ENTER ANY CD KEY UNDER INSTALLATION!, and chose ultimate)
3. Apply the crack and test if ist working (right-click Computer and goto Properties)
4. If crack is working, start downloading all the updates (find the Windows Update tool in start menu)
5. Install the Service Pack.
6. Enjoy your new legal Windows Vista Ultimate 64-bit Danish!
